{"word":"ἀνθάπτομαι","slug":"ἀνθάπτομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνθάπτομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to lay hold of in turn</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>simply <i>to lay hold of, grapple with, engage in</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: generally, <i>to reach, attain</i>, <el>τερμόνων</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to lay hold of, attack</i>, <el>πλευμόνων, φρενῶν</el>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}